00:02:34.120 --> 00:02:38.970
If you have followed all previous steps, this
goal will be easily accomplished.

00:02:38.970 --> 00:02:44.120
Not doing so will create an incorrect and
inferior dining experience and thus will not

00:02:44.120 --> 00:02:47.450
